languages.text: "На твоей территории действовала ячейка мутантов-заговорщиков. Они были вооружены авторужьями и без боя не сдались".
"A secret cell of mutant conspirators was operating in your jurisdiction. They were armed with autoguns and refused to surrender peacefully."

languages.text: «Una célula secreta de conspiradores mutantes operaba en su jurisdicción. Estaban armados con rifles automáticos y se negaron a rendirse pacíficamente».
languages.original_text: "A secret cell of mutant conspirators was operating in your jurisdiction. They were armed with autoguns and refused to surrender peacefully."

traits.locale_text: «Una célula secreta de conspiradores mutantes operaba en su jurisdicción. Estaban armados con ametralladoras y se negaron a rendirse pacíficamente».

languages.text: 「変異体共謀者の秘密組織はお前の管轄区域で活動していた。奴らはオートガンで武装していて、平和的降伏を拒否したのだ」
languages.original_text: "A secret cell of mutant conspirators was operating in your jurisdiction. They were armed with autoguns and refused to surrender peacefully."

traits.locale_text: 「変異体共謀者の秘密組織はお前の管轄区域で活動していた。奴らはスタッバーで武装していて、平和的幸福を拒否したのだ」

languages.text: “一群变种人叛乱分子在你管辖的区域里组建了秘密组织。他们配备了自动枪，不肯放下武器投降。”
languages.original_text: "A secret cell of mutant conspirators was operating in your jurisdiction. They were armed with autoguns and refused to surrender peacefully."

traits.locale_text: “一群变种人叛乱分子在你管辖的区域里组建了秘密组织。他们配备了伐木枪，不肯放下武器投降。”

languages.text: "Eine geheime Zelle von Mutantenverschwörern hat in Eurem Zuständigkeitsbereich operiert. Sie waren mit Sturmgewehren bewaffnet und wollten sich nicht friedlich ergeben."
languages.original_text: "A secret cell of mutant conspirators was operating in your jurisdiction. They were armed with autoguns and refused to surrender peacefully."

traits.locale_text: "Eine geheime Zelle von Mutantenverschwörern hat in Eurem Zuständigkeitsbereich operiert. Sie waren mit Maschinengewehren bewaffnet und wollten sich nicht friedlich ergeben."

languages.text: « Nous avons découvert une cellule secrète de conspirateurs mutants dans votre juridiction. Ils étaient armés de fusils d'assaut et ont refusé de se rendre sans combattre. »
languages.original_text: "A secret cell of mutant conspirators was operating in your jurisdiction. They were armed with autoguns and refused to surrender peacefully."

traits.locale_text: « Nous avons découvert une cellule secrète de conspirateurs mutants dans votre juridiction. Ils étaient armés de mitrailleuses et ont refusé de se rendre sans combattre. »

languages.text: "Komplocu mutantlardan oluşan gizli bir hücre, yetki alanın içinde faaliyet gösteriyordu. Ototüfek kuşanmışlardı ve olaysız bir şekilde teslim olmayı reddettiler."
